name: Apple Inc.
description: A multinational technology company that designs, manufactures, and markets smartphones, personal computers, tablets, wearables, and accessories, along with a variety of related services.

name: Microsoft Corporation
description: A technology company that develops, licenses, and supports software products, services, and devices, including operating systems, productivity software, server applications, and cloud services.

name: Amazon.com, Inc.
description: A multinational technology company focusing on e-commerce, cloud computing, digital streaming, and artificial intelligence, operating the world's largest online marketplace.

name: Alphabet Inc.
description: A multinational technology conglomerate that specializes in Internet-related services and products, including online advertising technologies, search engine, cloud computing, software, and hardware.

name: Meta Platforms, Inc.
description: A technology company that builds technologies to connect people through social media platforms, communication apps, and augmented/virtual reality products.

name: Tesla, Inc.
description: An electric vehicle and clean energy company that designs and manufactures electric cars, battery energy storage systems, solar panels, and related products and services.

name: NVIDIA Corporation
description: A technology company specializing in designing graphics processing units (GPUs) for gaming, professional visualization, data centers, and artificial intelligence applications.

name: JPMorgan Chase & Co.
description: A multinational investment bank and financial services holding company offering investment banking, financial services for consumers and small businesses, commercial banking, and asset management.

name: Johnson & Johnson
description: A multinational corporation that develops medical devices, pharmaceuticals, and consumer packaged goods, with a focus on research and development of innovative healthcare products.

name: The Procter & Gamble Company
description: A multinational consumer goods corporation that specializes in a wide range of personal health, consumer health, personal care and hygiene products organized into several segments.
